            <p class=3D"detaildesc">
              Please note :<br>Advert for whole property not individual roo=
ms.<br>Bill's are not included <br><br>This 3-bedroom flat located on Bow C=
ommon Lane in Mile End, E3, offers a practical and comfortable living envir=
onment. The property includes two well-appointed bathrooms and a single rec=
eption room, providing ample space for relaxation and entertainment. The mo=
dern kitchen is equipped with essential appliances, including a washing mac=
hine and oven, set against sleek black tile backsplash and white cabinetry,=
 creating a contemporary feel.<br><br>The living area is bright and welcomi=
ng, featuring wooden flooring that extends throughout the property, enhanci=
ng the sense of space and continuity. Each bedroom is designed to maximize =
comfort, with large windows allowing for plenty of natural light. The bathr=
ooms are fitted with modern fixtures, with one offering a bathtub and the o=
ther a shower enclosure, catering to diverse preferences.<br><br>While the =
property does not include designated parking or a private outdoor space, it=
s location in Mile End offers convenient access to a range of amenities. Th=
e area is well-served by public transport, with nearby stations providing e=
asy connections to the rest of London. Local shops, cafes, and parks are wi=
thin walking distance, making it a practical choice for those seeking a bal=
ance of urban living and community atmosphere.<br><br>The property is avail=
able for rent with flexible furnishing options, allowing tenants to persona=
lize the space to their liking. This flat is ideal for individuals or famil=
ies looking for a well-connected and comfortable home in the vibrant Mile E=
nd area.
            </p>
